Set up:
$ cd xmlrpc-c-1.25.26
$ ./configure --prefix=../rpc
$ make
$ make install
$ cd ../code
$ make
$ export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=../rpc/lib

If something breaks, change XMLRPC_C_CONFIG in your Makefile.

Run:
Server - 
$ ./xmlrpc_sample_add_server 8080 &
$ ./xmlrpc_sample_add_server 8081 &
$ ./xmlrpc_sample_add_server 8082 &

Sync Client - 
$ ./xmlrpc_sample_add_client

Async Client -
$ ./xmlrpc_asynch_client